last_episode_to_air.overview: Eleven-year-old Katy Carr is a lively daredevil older sister in a big family. Her dad now lives with Izzie, but Katy cannot forget her mum, who died some years previously. Katy keeps getting in trouble everywhere, especially with her stepmum Izzie! After Katy suffers a serious injury, will her life ever be the same again?
